.TH "TODOPRO RAMBLE" "1" "2026-02-27" "1.0.0" "todopro ramble Manual"
.SH NAME
todopro\-ramble \- Ramble — voice-to-tasks
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B todopro ramble
[OPTIONS] COMMAND [ARGS]...
.SH DESCRIPTION
Ramble — voice-to-tasks
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-d,\fP \-\-duration INTEGER
Recording duration in seconds  [default: 30]
.TP
\fB\-\-stt\fP TEXT
STT provider (whisper/gemini/deepgram)  [default: whisper]
.TP
\fB\-\-llm\fP TEXT
LLM provider (gemini/openai)  [default: gemini]
.TP
\fB\-\-project\fP TEXT
Default project for tasks
.TP
\fB\-\-dry\-run\fP
Show parsed tasks without creating
.TP
\fB\-l,\fP \-\-language TEXT
Language code (auto/en/vi/...)  [default: auto]
.TP
\fB\-\-stream\fP
Streaming mode (premium, cloud context required)
.TP
\fB\-\-text\fP TEXT
Use text transcript instead of microphone (no mic required)
.SH COMMANDS
.PP
\fBhistory\fP
  Show Ramble session history.
  See \fBtodopro ramble-history(1)\fP for full documentation on the \fBhistory\fP command.
.PP
\fBconfig\fP
  Show or update Ramble configuration.
  See \fBtodopro ramble-config(1)\fP for full documentation on the \fBconfig\fP command.
.PP
\fBusage\fP
  Show Ramble usage stats for today.
  See \fBtodopro ramble-usage(1)\fP for full documentation on the \fBusage\fP command.
